<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们围在井边，一言不发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们已经同意了各自许两个愿望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在只有潘瑟剩下一个愿望可以许了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要在这里站上一整天吗？”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的声音听上去有点儿不高兴了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊用胳膊肘推了推潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“轮到你了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟点点头，但却没有说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们的愿望都要用完了吗？”休伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟依然没有说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比大声叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简轻轻地用脚踢了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊转了转脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们显然都有点儿烦了，但没人说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望每个人都可以说出他心里想的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟突然不假思索地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊的鳍开始一开一合。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟用手捂住了嘴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，休伊。那不是一个愿望。”她叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但你许愿了啊！”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鳍变成了紫色和蓝色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的意思是……”潘瑟试图解释，但已经太迟了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊实现了她的愿望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在离开这里吧。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊将休伊放到了木桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他慢慢把休伊送回井底时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊轻声说：“我真的厌倦了每次都做这件事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的兄弟姐妹们盯着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊猛地用手捂住了嘴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我为什么说出来了？”他惊奇地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是因为你很刻薄。”简喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她随后也用手捂住了嘴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们突然感觉面对彼此很尴尬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我们应该回家了。”潘瑟建议说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们走出了森林。潘瑟领头走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她有很多事情需要思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，赛伊从后面叫住了她：“你能不能慢一点？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟转头嚷道：“你干吗不走快点？你真慢！"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真慢？你说谁慢？”赛伊叫嚷着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你总是觉得你比我们都强！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我本来就是！”潘瑟叫嚷着回击。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你俩都住嘴！”鲍比爆发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和赛伊都吃惊地盯着他们的弟弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你让我住嘴？”赛伊生气地问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！你俩就像两只猴子！”鲍比叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看上去才像只猴子呢！”简对着鲍比大嚷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快四个孩子都相互叫骂了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以这才是你们对我真正的看法。”潘瑟哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还以为你们关心我。”鲍比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，孩子们都没话要说了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是最糟糕的愿望。”简抽着鼻子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟一句话都没说，因为在她的心里也是同意的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们相互不再说话，都沉默着继续往家走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们接近镇子的时候，孩子们听到了到处都在尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我讨厌你！”基弗先生对着一个年轻女人嚷嚷着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，我也从来没有喜欢过你！”那个女人反击道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，孩子们看到了带着兰姆的玛莎阿姨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在和农夫詹金斯的妻子说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的发型太丑了！”詹金斯夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”玛莎阿姨摸了摸头发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧， 你的裙子看上去就像渔夫！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是吗？那总比你穿的像个老太太好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>詹金斯夫人大叫。这两个女人看上去就要打起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟向他们跑过去。“你们不是那个意思的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她恳求地说，“你们两个是朋友啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她才不是我的朋友！”玛莎阿姨大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她绝对不是我朋友！”詹金斯夫人叫嚷着回击。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟的眼里充满了泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我都干了些什么？”她哀叹道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>